RAD_DATASOURCES.DEFAULT_WHERE: EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM LBTB_TRADE_PROCESSING_QUEUE WHERE TRANCHE_REF_NO = CONTRACT_REF_NO AND (NVL(PENDING_SSI, 'N') = 'Y' OR NVL(PROCESS_STATUS, 'X') <> 'P')) OR EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM LBTB_AGENCY_CONFIRM_BROWSER WHERE TRANCHE_REF_NO = CONTRACT_REF_NO AND CONFIRMATION_STATUS = 'P' AND PROCESS_STATUS = 'E' AND NVL(MESSAGE_STATUS, 'X') = DECODE(TRADE_SOURCE, 'CLEARPAR', 'X', 'MARKIT', 'P'))

PARTICIPANT NOT IN (SELECT COUNTERPARTY FROM LBTB_PART_PROC_STAT WHERE BORROWER_REF_NO = LBTB_UPLOAD_NEW_PARTICIPANT.CONTRACT_REF_NO) AND (EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM LBTB_TRADE_PROCESSING_QUEUE WHERE TRANCHE_REF_NO = CONTRACT_REF_NO AND (NVL(PENDING_SSI, 'N') = 'Y') AND TRANSFEREE = PARTICIPANT) OR EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM LBTB_AGENCY_CONFIRM_BROWSER WHERE tranche_ref_no = contract_ref_no AND confirmation_status = 'P' AND process_status = 'E' and NVL(message_status, 'X') = DECODE(trade_source, 'CLEARPAR', 'X', 'MARKIT', 'P')))

RAD_DATASOURCES.RELATION_WITH_PARENT: LBTBS_UPLOAD_NEW_PARTICIPANT.PARTICIPANT = LBTBS_UPLOAD_NEW_PART_CURR.PARTICIPANT AND LBTBS_UPLOAD_NEW_PARTICIPANT.CONTRACT_REF_NO = LBTBS_UPLOAD_NEW_PART_CURR.CONTRACT_REF_NO and LBTBS_UPLOAD_NEW_PARTICIPANT.UPLOAD_SEQ_NO = LBTBS_UPLOAD_NEW_PART_CURR.UPLOAD_SEQ_NO and LBTBS_UPLOAD_NEW_PARTICIPANT.SOURCE_CODE = LBTBS_UPLOAD_NEW_PART_CURR.SOURCE_CODE and LBTBS_UPLOAD_NEW_PARTICIPANT.BRANCH = LBTBS_UPLOAD_NEW_PART_CURR.BRANCH and LBTBS_UPLOAD_NEW_PARTICIPANT.EXT_CONTRACT_REF_NO = LBTBS_UPLOAD_NEW_PART_CURR.EXT_CONTRACT_REF_NO

LBTBS_UPLOAD_NEW_PARTICIPANT.CONTRACT_REF_NO = LBTBS_UPLOAD_NEW_PART_ENTITY.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND LBTBS_UPLOAD_NEW_PARTICIPANT.UPLOAD_SEQ_NO = LBTBS_UPLOAD_NEW_PART_ENTITY.UPLOAD_SEQ_NO AND LBTBS_UPLOAD_NEW_PARTICIPANT.PARTICIPANT = LBTBS_UPLOAD_NEW_PART_ENTITY.PARTICIPANT AND LBTBS_UPLOAD_NEW_PARTICIPANT.SOURCE_CODE = LBTBS_UPLOAD_NEW_PART_ENTITY.SOURCE_CODE AND LBTBS_UPLOAD_NEW_PARTICIPANT.BRANCH = LBTBS_UPLOAD_NEW_PART_ENTITY.BRANCH AND LBTBS_UPLOAD_NEW_PARTICIPANT.EXT_CONTRACT_REF_NO = LBTBS_UPLOAD_NEW_PART_ENTITY.EXT_CONTRACT_REF_NO

RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT contract_ref_no,currency,auth_stat FROM LBTB_TRADE_PART_MNEMONIC WHERE exists (select 1 from lbtbs_trade_processing_queue where tranche_ref_no = contract_ref_no and (NVL(pending_ssi, 'N') = 'Y' or nvl(process_status, 'x') <> 'P')) or exists (select 1 from lbtbs_agency_confirm_browser where tranche_ref_no = contract_ref_no and confirmation_status = 'P' and process_status = 'E' and NVL(message_status, 'X') = DECODE(trade_source, 'CLEARPAR', 'X', 'MARKIT', 'P'))

SELECT distinct c.ccy_code, c.ccy_name FROM CYTMS_CCY_DEFN c, LBTBS_BORROWER_CCY l WHERE c.ccy_code = l.ccy AND l.contract_ref_no = ? AND l.ccy not in (SELECT currency FROM LBTB_UPLOAD_NEW_PART_CURR a WHERE a.contract_ref_no = ? AND a.participant = ?)

SELECT ssi_mnemonic,settlement_seq_no,counterparty, (SELECT customer_name1 FROM OLTMS_CUSTOMER WHERE customer_no = a.counterparty),currency, product_code,module, branch, pay_ac_branch,pay_account,pay_account_ccy,recv_ac_branch,recv_account, recv_account_ccy FROM OLTM_INSTR a WHERE counterparty IN (?, 'ALL') AND Currency IN (?, '*.*') AND branch IN (sypks_utils.get_branch(?), 'ALL') AND module IN ('LB', 'AL') AND product_code IN (sypks_utils.get_product(?), 'ALL') AND a.record_stat = 'O' AND a.auth_stat = 'A'

SELECT a.entity, a.entity_name, a.entity_type FROM OLTMS_CUSTOMER_ENTITY_DETAILS a WHERE a.customer_no = ? AND a.entity NOT IN (SELECT entity_id FROM LBTB_UPLOAD_NEW_PART_ENTITY b WHERE b.contract_ref_no = ? AND b.participant = ? AND b.entity_id = a.entity)
